-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Includes deep cuts of all available Data Romance music for the collector, 
  including FKA "Names" and Ajay's side project "STINT"
- Data Romance - "Other" album intentionally not included, except free tracks.
  Support them by buying their newest album off Amazon, Google Play, or iTunes
- Life Cycles OST, Caves Singles, Data Romance EP obtained from Amazon MP3
- Covers, STINT, most remixes, and some singled obtained from SoundCloud
- Names - Paint obtained from iTunes
- Christmas songs, Live in Studio, interviews, other remixes & singles stripped 
  from Youtube, Vimeo, or obtained elsewhere online
- AAC Audio from videos was copied, not reencoded.
- The highest bitrate possible was obtained, but some have been lossily reencoded
- Some original files from CargoCollective and other sources are longer available
  If you have, please message MosesCleaveland @ TPB or M_Cleaveland @ KAT
- Miss Angie included as she the closest Christian artist, although more rock
 &
- Clueless, Weird Science, & Beauty and the Geek torrents included because:
